NodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "8c8f726c-1b12-4060-972e-87a315fffdc0", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "a62fd841f0c91bb3b7c3019630040af08d39fa80bb64e7e7c2507cac5bc500ae", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "bb29f674-3850-4f7b-b1ec-45cfd9d7ddbe", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "5a39a49d4774832e6f122866387fd64a9c249c37cffc08db4e3430b386faa898", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "1 No Use: Recipient agrees not to use the Confidential Information in any way or under any circumstances share the same, in writing or through any other means, with any Third Party.2.2 No Unauthorized Disclosure: Recipient agrees to use its best efforts to prevent and protect the Confidential Information, or any part thereof, from disclosure to any person(s) or entity (ies), even if authorized or directed under any law, without the express permission of the Discloser.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 1454, "end_char_idx": 1926, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "bb29f674-3850-4f7b-b1ec-45cfd9d7ddbe": {"__data__": {"id_": "bb29f674-3850-4f7b-b1ec-45cfd9d7ddbe", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "71d5969d-71e7-49a1-83f1-eb1b867e884e", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "368fce13f3dc6c0b562c9384dfc467ec2ebaaa15e2cfbf1c87cfdfa010263c97", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "0000f927-c6b8-428f-be2a-ce058ad2f2c3", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "632d0c6508becba16627e7e0afbe431b6d7c01bd47930a609479172189763aea", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "5a4c6d0b-1740-43f7-9e19-ad1c9ed209cf", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "f0e637da9c9b065374b13070fc1be1cac4485bb11b57da1f50be4e8c15dbebf5", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "Discloser, notwithstanding, shall have the right to  deny  such  disclosure  of  the  Confidential  Information  being  detrimental  to  the security interests of the Discloser and/or its\n2.3 Protection of Secrecy: Recipient agrees to take all steps necessary to protect the secrecy of the Confidential Information, and to prevent the Confidential Information from failing into the public domain or into the possession of unauthorized person(s) and/or entity(ies).2.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 1929, "end_char_idx": 2395, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "5a4c6d0b-1740-43f7-9e19-ad1c9ed209cf": {"__data__": {"id_": "5a4c6d0b-1740-43f7-9e19-ad1c9ed209cf", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "71d5969d-71e7-49a1-83f1-eb1b867e884e", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "368fce13f3dc6c0b562c9384dfc467ec2ebaaa15e2cfbf1c87cfdfa010263c97", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "bb29f674-3850-4f7b-b1ec-45cfd9d7ddbe", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "5a39a49d4774832e6f122866387fd64a9c249c37cffc08db4e3430b386faa898", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "b52e13bb-dc37-4d2e-9365-71b2e2d1406f", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "941ad047b8b7c8237ef3896cc854d19f086b08026578893b816badeee2dd118a", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "4 Recipient agrees that the layout plan of the structural design of the Premises, whether  in  in  physical  or  electronic  form,  shall  always  be  in  the  custody  of  the Discloser.  However,  the  Recipient  shall  have  the  access  to  the  layout  plan  for  the purpose of carrying out the contract for installation of CCTV System.3.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 2397, "end_char_idx": 2741, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "b52e13bb-dc37-4d2e-9365-71b2e2d1406f": {"__data__": {"id_": "b52e13bb-dc37-4d2e-9365-71b2e2d1406f", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "71d5969d-71e7-49a1-83f1-eb1b867e884e", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "368fce13f3dc6c0b562c9384dfc467ec2ebaaa15e2cfbf1c87cfdfa010263c97", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "5a4c6d0b-1740-43f7-9e19-ad1c9ed209cf", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "f0e637da9c9b065374b13070fc1be1cac4485bb11b57da1f50be4e8c15dbebf5", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "92f0e00e-3e6e-409c-9fb2-ff841cecf698", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "11ce77eee58854f8a1e6abf7108b9bc2a3dcae719125308ba803432b4a05916d", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "Notices: All notices hereunder shall be given by letter, addressed as follows:\n\n4. Term  and  Termination.\n\n The  term  of  this  Agreement  shall  commence  on  the\nEffective Date i.e. the date of signing the Agreement for the Purpose and continue for such a period until and unless the Discloser terminates the Agreement or the Premises is relocated or vacated or abandoned, whichever is earlier.\n\n5. Breach.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 2744, "end_char_idx": 3154, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "92f0e00e-3e6e-409c-9fb2-ff841cecf698": {"__data__": {"id_": "92f0e00e-3e6e-409c-9fb2-ff841cecf698", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "71d5969d-71e7-49a1-83f1-eb1b867e884e", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "368fce13f3dc6c0b562c9384dfc467ec2ebaaa15e2cfbf1c87cfdfa010263c97", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "b52e13bb-dc37-4d2e-9365-71b2e2d1406f", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "941ad047b8b7c8237ef3896cc854d19f086b08026578893b816badeee2dd118a", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "3284de2e-2ed4-4c98-8da3-2a194ffab416", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "345019a0e3bab57e640a3ce474afe868eb62e957c92043014cfac5f4035cf557", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "The  Recipient  acknowledges  that  disclosure  or  use  of  Confidential Information  in  violation  of  this  Agreement  could  cause  irreparable  harm  to Discloser  including  loss  of  lives  and  limbs  of  the  persons  and  damage  to  the property, for which monetary damages may be difficult to ascertain or turn to be meaningless.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 3157, "end_char_idx": 3499, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "3284de2e-2ed4-4c98-8da3-2a194ffab416": {"__data__": {"id_": "3284de2e-2ed4-4c98-8da3-2a194ffab416", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "71d5969d-71e7-49a1-83f1-eb1b867e884e", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "368fce13f3dc6c0b562c9384dfc467ec2ebaaa15e2cfbf1c87cfdfa010263c97", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "92f0e00e-3e6e-409c-9fb2-ff841cecf698", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "11ce77eee58854f8a1e6abf7108b9bc2a3dcae719125308ba803432b4a05916d", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "4f33e3eb-0ea3-4e0a-9140-b55d0cb49ccc", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "643c98ca172eeeb624f236c1cd38f3d8593ddb56e96e09568dbc72d08712d1bc", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "The Recipient therefore agrees that Discloser will have the right, in addition to its other rights and remedies, to seek injunctive relief for violations of this Agreement.\n\n6. In case the Discloser suspects any violation of this Agreement, upon reasonable notice,\n\n it shall be binding for the Recipient to allow the Discloser to carry out an Audit by itself or by an authorized representative. In such a situation, the Recipient shall cooperate with the Discloser.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 3502, "end_char_idx": 3968, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "4f33e3eb-0ea3-4e0a-9140-b55d0cb49ccc": {"__data__": {"id_": "4f33e3eb-0ea3-4e0a-9140-b55d0cb49ccc", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "71d5969d-71e7-49a1-83f1-eb1b867e884e", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "368fce13f3dc6c0b562c9384dfc467ec2ebaaa15e2cfbf1c87cfdfa010263c97", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "3284de2e-2ed4-4c98-8da3-2a194ffab416", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "345019a0e3bab57e640a3ce474afe868eb62e957c92043014cfac5f4035cf557", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "563bea55-c53c-4ba0-97bc-c3b5e83523df", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "69c24ee95ed69ccf4da2179c70ae056d54bc9d3c6be24d8b18cb48edc6cb2d02", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "The onus to rebut the suspicion shall lie on the Recipient\n\n\n[Name of the Mission/Post] [Address] Attention [Insert Name] Title:[Insert Designation] E- mail:[Insert E-mail] Telephone:[Insert Number] Fax:[Insert Number] [Name of the Company] [Address] Attention:[Insert Name] Title: [Insert Designation] E- mail:[Insert E-mail] Telephone: [Insert Number] Fax: [Insert Number]\n\n7.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 3969, "end_char_idx": 4347, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "563bea55-c53c-4ba0-97bc-c3b5e83523df": {"__data__": {"id_": "563bea55-c53c-4ba0-97bc-c3b5e83523df", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "71d5969d-71e7-49a1-83f1-eb1b867e884e", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "368fce13f3dc6c0b562c9384dfc467ec2ebaaa15e2cfbf1c87cfdfa010263c97", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "4f33e3eb-0ea3-4e0a-9140-b55d0cb49ccc", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "643c98ca172eeeb624f236c1cd38f3d8593ddb56e96e09568dbc72d08712d1bc", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "dd5fcc46-cf09-4f95-83ee-1b73e2f568c8", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "24cbc3169f9fe16ecba1b89e1c952eda967b03808386eea27d5823115b24503d", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "Any dispute or difference arising out of or in connection with this Non- Discloser Agreement shall be setteled amicably by the Parties through mutual negotiations. Any  unsettled  dispute  or  difference  shall  be  referred  to  Arbitration  by  a  Sole Arbitrator. The Arbitration shall be conducted in accordance with the rules and procedure  of  UNCITRAL  in  force  on  the  date  of  Agreement.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 4350, "end_char_idx": 4750, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "dd5fcc46-cf09-4f95-83ee-1b73e2f568c8": {"__data__": {"id_": "dd5fcc46-cf09-4f95-83ee-1b73e2f568c8", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "71d5969d-71e7-49a1-83f1-eb1b867e884e", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "ha